{"tid":433153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人大過咗 易病咗好多？","createTime":"2017-10-12T06:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T10:05:22.000Z","uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"252f637915ffa7647c8a0451e14cc9a97160ce1e","tid":433153,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"以前正值青春期<br />\n由細到大一年都病唔到一次 <br />\n就算係病都好快好返 一日起兩日止<br />\n覺得自己好似抵抗力好強 百毒不侵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過依家個人大咗 其實都只係講緊廿中<br />\n但今年都未完<br />\n已經病左四五次<br />\n次次都好感覺好難好返<br />\n有次仲病足成個星期<br />\n完全感受到身體抵抗力差左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁？見到自己身體咁樣好似已經不再年輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc4cfb030adce66151c59bc0709e5978e68d360","tid":433153,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:51:17.000Z","msg":"幾歲？"},{"pid":"78988819eb009c4ea859216383ff737233cc8ea7","tid":433153,"uid":122807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"可能係你忙左,運動少左?"}]}